{"id":1220,"date":"2025-04-10T01:08:52","date_gmt":"2025-04-09T18:08:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?post_type=product&#038;p=1220"},"modified":"2025-11-25T09:39:54","modified_gmt":"2025-11-25T02:39:54","slug":"tach-day-va-laser-seo","status":"publish","type":"product","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/tach-day-va-laser-seo\/","title":{"rendered":"T\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1y v\u00e0 laser s\u1eb9o"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho da s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u00f3ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m \u0111\u00e1y vu\u00f4ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng ch\u00e2n kim.<\/em><\/p>\n<h3><em>L\u1ee3i \u00edch ch\u00ednh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\u0110\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1eebng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u00f4 s\u1eb9o, kh\u00f4ng x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f9ng da xung quanh.<\/li>\n<li>B\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e1i t\u1ea1o trong th\u1eddi gian ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p, kho\u1ebb m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u00e0u.<\/li>\n<li>S\u1ea3n sinh Collagen m\u1edbi thay th\u1ebf c\u00e1c t\u1ebf b\u00e0o c\u0169.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p t\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1y ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 c\u00e1c s\u1ee3i li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u1edbi ch\u00e2n s\u1eb9o, m\u00f4 s\u1eb9o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ea7y gi\u00fap li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh laser s\u1eb9o chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. \u1ee8ng d\u1ee5ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 laser CO\u2082 Fractional \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ecb chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c t\u1eebng t\u1ebf b\u00e0o m\u00f4 s\u1eb9o, ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 li\u00ean k\u1ebft v\u00e0 b\u00f3c t\u00e1ch t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c m\u00f4 s\u1eb9o d\u01b0\u1edbi da, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0m s\u1eb9o l\u1ed3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n, ng\u0103n ng\u1eeba t\u00e1i ph\u00e1t sau li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh.<\/li>\n<li>Duy tr\u00ec c\u00f9ng GSC Ultra Calming K Cream ch\u1ee9a ph\u1ee9c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed9c quy\u1ec1n (Pro Anti-Irritant Complex) g\u1ed3m Vitamin K, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t c\u00fac La M\u00e3 v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt gi\u00fap l\u00e0m l\u00e0nh nhanh t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng da sau x\u00e2m l\u1ea5n.<\/li>\n<li>K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi b\u1ed9 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da d\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho da s\u1eb9o t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0, m\u1edd th\u00e2m, c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t da, t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><em>Th\u1eddi gian li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh:<\/em><\/h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 01 &#8211; 02 ti\u1ebfng (tu\u1ef3 v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng s\u1eb9o).<\/li>\n<li>M\u1ed9t li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng 05 bu\u1ed5i, kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eeb 21 &#8211; 28 ng\u00e0y, trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00e1ch nhau 14 ng\u00e0y.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<div id=\"gtx-trans\" style=\"position: absolute; left: -7px; top: 43.4062px;\">\n<div class=\"gtx-trans-icon\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p><em>Li\u1ec7u tr\u00ecnh chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t d\u00e0nh cho da s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3n s\u00f3ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m \u0111\u00e1y vu\u00f4ng, s\u1eb9o l\u00f5m d\u1ea1ng ch\u00e2n kim.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":3586,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"product_brand":[],"product_cat":[58],"product_tag":[],"class_list":{"0":"post-1220","1":"product","2":"type-product","3":"status-publish","4":"has-post-thumbnail","6":"product_cat-laser","8":"first","9":"instock","10":"virtual","11":"product-type-simple"},"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product\/1220","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/product"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/g